 Multithreading ek technique hai jisme ek program me Thread ke sath execute kar sakte hai 
 or yah program ke execution ko fast karne ke liye use hota hai 
  
 Thread - Thread ek light weight sub process hoti hai jo ek sath multiple task ko execute kar sakti hai
 
 Java me MultiThreading ko implement karne ke Two ways hai
 1-	Thread Class
 2- Runnable Interface 
 
 Thread class - Thread class me start() method run() method ko automatic call Akrta hai or ek new Thread create Krta hai
 Runnable Interface - Runnable Interface Jyada flexible hota hai becouse hm ise 
 						java ki kisi or class ko bhi extends kar skte h 
 						
 						
 Thread ke Important Method
 
 start() - Thread execution ko start krta hai
 run() - Thread ka task execute Krta hai
 sleep() -Thread ko kuch time ke liye rokta hai
 join()- Current thread ko tab tak roka rhega jab tak dusra thread execute nhi hota
 setPriority(int p) - Thread ki priority set karta hai (MIN_PRIORITY=1, NORM_PRIORITY=5, MAX_PRIORITY=10)	
 getName() - Thread ka name return karta hai	
 
 
 
 Feature	   		Multitasking	                            Multithreading
Definition			ek time me kayi processes ko execute करना	 | एक process के अंदर कई threads को execute करना
Resource Usage		हर process को अलग memory मिलती है	   |   सभी threads एक ही memory share करते हैं
Context Switching	Slow						|		Fast
Example	एक साथ Chrome, VS Code, और Spotify चलाना	   |    एक ही application में background sync और UI update
 	 
 
 